Or we feel like something, we have
done it.And then it gets very messy.

23:41.626 --> 23:44.421
So, please pay attention to this.

23:44.421 --> 23:45.821
Whatever work is given to a man

23:46.071 --> 23:48.871
The more he wins responsibly,
the more he will benefit.

23:48.871 --> 23:51.122
And their troubles will be less.

23:51.122 --> 23:56.332
We hope that all of us will do
Sahaja Yoga with understanding and

23:58.082 --> 23:59.532
More wisely.

23:59.556 --> 24:02.181
By the way, all of you are my children

24:02.181 --> 24:04.581
And I love you all very much.

24:05.831 --> 24:08.331
And do not want to say more than this,

24:08.331 --> 24:12.341
To hurt you.

24:13.141 --> 24:15.391
But it should be understood that

24:15.391 --> 24:18.391
it is more important
to handle responsibility.

24:18.391 --> 24:19.441
And I would have

24:20.841 --> 24:25.051
meditated on you for thousands
of years and stood before them.

24:25.051 --> 24:31.101
So there could have been some other Sahaja
Yoga place. Which has very Rich people.

24:31.101 --> 24:36.401
I will stay in Delhi for a few
days and work hard on you here.

24:39.052 --> 26:15.971
Waiting for Mr.Chandrika Prasad
Srivastava (Mataji's Husband)

26:15.971 --> 27:26.621
(Welcomed from delhi with flowers )

27:26.621 --> 31:31.871
(A Sahaja Yogi gave a
speech praising both of them )

31:31.871 --> 31:41.131
(Awaiting Mr.Chandrika
Prasad Srivastava's speech)

31:50.241 --> 31:52.351
My dear Sahaja Yogis.

31:53.751 --> 31:54.751
Today is

31:56.251 --> 31:58.751
very important for me,

31:58.751 --> 32:01.051
it is also for you.

32:01.851 --> 32:04.351
But first I want to tell you that,

32:05.501 --> 32:07.151
It has been 43 years.

32:07.151 --> 32:10.651
I was married to

32:10.651 --> 32:15.451
your mother on 07-04-1947

32:22.203 --> 32:25.013
And we have been together for 43 years.

32:26.815 --> 32:28.960
And she has been watching
me and looking at herself

32:31.813 --> 32:36.323
So, first of all I want to
show my gratitude to her.

32:42.323 --> 32:48.073
Dr. Nigam Saheb said
that she should stay with me.

32:48.073 --> 32:53.933
Most of the time Husband and
wife stay together,that is fine.

32:53.933 --> 33:00.632
But you took her
time By separating us .

33:01.632 --> 33:06.085
But I want to tell you that she
can not separated from me.

33:12.333 --> 33:15.643
Where does she live with
you? she lives in your heart.

33:16.645 --> 33:18.441
by the way, it is always in my heart.

33:24.903 --> 33:29.353
And she is everywhere. she is
with everyone. She is always with me.

33:30.404 --> 33:36.655
This is what Adishakti means. Full
power is everywhere with everyone.

33:41.415 --> 33:45.965
In these 43 years we did many things.

33:45.965 --> 33:49.015
Many countries we went around the world.

33:49.015 --> 33:55.122
But I want to tell you like you
are seeing her as a mother here.

33:55.122 --> 33:56.672
She is your Mother.

33:56.672 --> 33:59.072
Like that all over the world,

33:59.072 --> 34:04.958
In China, in Japan, in
Argentina, in Sydney, in

34:04.983 --> 34:10.722
Australia every were
they considered as mother.

34:17.383 --> 34:20.983
Today we are with you on
our wedding anniversary.

34:22.243 --> 34:23.493
My daughters are not here.

34:23.493 --> 34:24.743
but

34:25.894 --> 34:28.394
Today, Dr. Nigam has
given me a very big title.

34:29.694 --> 34:32.694
Perhaps I have never received or
ever received such a big title before.

34:33.344 --> 34:34.844
He called me Dad.

34:42.254 --> 34:44.904
Now how big a family has become mine.

34:44.904 --> 34:48.554
And We are with you right now.so
it's felt like i'm with my Children.

34:55.051 --> 34:56.865
You know the love of mother.

34:58.012 --> 35:01.513
But Papa's love does not
diminish.Does not happen like this.

35:09.062 --> 35:13.823
How can I show my love to you people?

35:14.872 --> 35:17.522
I just want to tell you,

35:19.172 --> 35:23.922
That Sahaja Yoga is very
much needed in the world.

35:23.922 --> 35:27.432
But science is growing everywhere,

35:27.432 --> 35:29.731
technology is increasing.

35:30.733 --> 35:35.632
A problem is occurring every
day. accident is increasing.

35:35.632 --> 35:37.892
You see how fast the airplanes are flying.

35:39.393 --> 35:42.291
Wherever they are seeing
something new is coming.

35:42.291 --> 35:43.692
Atom bomb,

35:44.692 --> 35:46.842
But in humans

35:47.992 --> 35:49.894
Does he changed ? Does he improved ?

35:49.894 --> 35:56.301
You can see that as much development
is happening.The less people look happy.

35:56.301 --> 36:00.802
Very few people i see happy
When I roam outside in foreign.

36:02.101 --> 36:03.602
Why they are not happy?

36:03.602 --> 36:08.001
They have a car, they have a freezer,
a refrigerator. what they don't have.

36:08.611 --> 36:10.611
But they are not happy.

36:11.261 --> 36:14.661
Because they don't have one thing
which is very big. Which is inward.

36:14.661 --> 36:17.563
She did not find it.They have lost it.

36:18.964 --> 36:23.614
And that is inner power. Your Power.

36:23.614 --> 36:29.225
And through Sahaja Yoga, that
power is being increased in you.

36:30.425 --> 36:33.925
And a new phase is beginning.

36:34.925 --> 36:36.225
And it is needed most.

36:36.225 --> 36:39.625
The biggest thing is important
for you that a person is good.

36:40.485 --> 36:42.985
But our country has a different problem.

36:43.635 --> 36:47.381
If we all become like this
"Like you". you're sitting.

36:47.381 --> 36:51.181
I call Sahajayogi as centers (kendr).

36:51.181 --> 36:54.084
Because they abandoning
all bad things , they only have

36:54.109 --> 36:56.831
truth, goodness and they
Come to the goodness side.

36:56.831 --> 37:00.091
If you see this kind of
people will be all around.

37:00.141 --> 37:01.891
So everything  can be improve.

