is a very important thing.

37:17.601 --> 37:20.401
And not only for you, it is
very important for the world.

37:20.803 --> 37:25.292
I understand because not everyone
is convinced, this is happening.

37:25.301 --> 37:28.911
That too is a miracle. she went
there. Just while ago She went there

37:28.911 --> 37:32.711
