As Dr. Nigam said.

38:05.584 --> 38:07.484
My only prayer to God  is

38:07.734 --> 38:10.134
They can also have a
daughter. (Talking to mother).

38:10.134 --> 38:13.091
My only request to God is to
increases Sahaja Yoga.and

38:13.116 --> 38:15.994
whatever service I can
do. I will definitely do that.

